data.eml:eml: Trilobites and agnostids from the Goyder Formation (Cambrian Series 3, Guzhangian, Mindyallan), Amadeus Basin, central Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Smith, Patrick M., Paterson, John R., Brock, Glenn A. (2018): Trilobites and agnostids from the Goyder Formation (Cambrian Series 3, Guzhangian, Mindyallan), Amadeus Basin, central Australia. Zootaxa 4396 (1): 1-67, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4396.1.1
